Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都柏林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利比里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 草间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像流浪汉一样的干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多久没来大学了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去了什么地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 长毛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我长毛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想接下来去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来？又要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是喜欢看地图研究下人类能去哪里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要骗我 大家都在说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样下去早晚会休学的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研讨班的金田都在叹息了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他联系下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流浪也要适可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别成了无根浮萍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样说...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 忘了东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在大学里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教员室在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 不吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连「江户名捕〇南 战栗的流星奏鸣曲」都不看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会说出那种话啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 别人有点事情拜托了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到那边去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去文学部的事又不是非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家只是「要是能过来帮忙一下就好了」的语气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以来帮忙吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要影响到天文部的活动准备的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么听到那番话后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易大家都...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文艺部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托我去给文化祭上出的文学杂志帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有暑假里联合活动结束后相关的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对这方面好像也不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明被我那样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你是作为天文部的使者被召唤了呢 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥梁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊 快阻止他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话 到那边去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过需要劳动力的时候要好好回来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 正所谓一石二鸟 老师很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 大家来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打气精神来 打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是拒绝掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从琴塚学姐那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天文部很不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从编辑到排版都是自己做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近还有是些名气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们文艺部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭也不只卖文学作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会邀请些作家 还有朗读会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在节目评比里也一直名列前茅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 最后决定这次发行2本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木来这边帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是标题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从星星的名字里选一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看到的是夏季的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织女星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼做VEGA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就VEGA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写做织女星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织女星 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然象征的是俯冲的鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为属于女性名词 听起来很柔和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯冲的鹰 写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么问题嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样再接再厉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 这里有点不大明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这里不是要分成三段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅啊 琴塚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文艺部其实还有别的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实都是琴塚学姐在主持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有人望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来 再多多努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了 我们希望天文部的人也写一篇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大八木君可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三藩市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯维加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这段时间就是天文部的基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面很普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice文化祭执行委 with 学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田 我理解你的心情 要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一个是一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草哥 圆顶呢 放这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用掉教室的大半？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室大概高3米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量利用的话直径是3~5米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能容纳10个人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投影机怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫针孔式天象仪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让光线通过小孔投射到周围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在厨房用的大碗上打上洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在下面放手电筒照亮就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实要做得像样的话还是挺难的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下 预算就是这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们平成骄子还有百元殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有信念 什么都能收集到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.90,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就买得到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢 那先去店里调查看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去买东西的话 我能先回下摄影部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 这和之前说的不大一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也是摄影部的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.54,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷静了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福啊 「小朔」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我们先去侦查了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那就开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封面女郎写真入手 还真是有难度的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是模特了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大八木君喜欢熟女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实的回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.43,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100円专区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大还是小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的哦 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟在做同样的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是不再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们不高兴点的话 小朔回来后会为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易草哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在去年是想都不敢想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 部长和草间老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是不准停车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模斯汉堡怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边今天只卖100円
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊 大家都回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉暑假已经是很遥远的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是来拿忘了的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 大八木君喜欢的颜色是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色？ 红色也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的食物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让问题来得更猛烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的女孩的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八州惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可逃不出我的金睛火眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着杂志时他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能作为参考
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传奇的大八木和二年级的小不点前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情纠纷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！\N大新闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去小夜那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天好像有点阴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 有点清甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹桂香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹桂花在喜马拉雅山上也会盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪闻到都是那么让人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你一直在转学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小美星那听说的哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在同一个公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会看书 伤都没好就转学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉卜力头的小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦都没想到会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很寂寞的哦 小美星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有草间老师在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也一定是调戏我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜喜喜喜欢什么的完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我指天文学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以再多了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学 astronomy这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是意为星星的astron和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名的意思的nemein组合而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个词已经产生了几千年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 无论哪个时代「给星星命名」这个原则从没改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}此处在讲冥王星被划出行星范围之事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给行星定义正是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你还会经历各种各样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会为这些知识和感情取名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是些怎样的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是卖弄了一下明野教授的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太欺负她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是对我来说很重要的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不由自主的就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我什么都没说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗啊 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把嘴巴封住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬 快听这些有的没的绯闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天运动部的人亲眼目睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在想熟女对策 突然就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛要瞎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝莓包买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜料不够了 红色红色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个笨蛋踩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 这让人泄气的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打洞第三次失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园顶也差好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞打坏了好像可以用锡补起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色幕布这么多够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不过这里好像没写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去交涉一下还能拿到2 3张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候最需要冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星就你最慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了部长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找执行委员的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 到处都像战场一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是印刷的预定日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天要派发的传单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经盖过章 就放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去了下文艺部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有天文部的人在帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很卖力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离文化祭还有一礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部的准备也要到最后阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你居然还同意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天文部的来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令营的活动也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 感冒了吗 脸很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说废话去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老等指示 自己找事做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了原稿去印刷室了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人 让你做了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 我一没注意他们就...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好教育他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自愿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也学到了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想那天也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野还有草间老师和你的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都传到学生会里来了 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我不会有什么奇怪的误解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:46.20,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要看...如此青涩的我 请不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很熟 但至少也认识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:50.93,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-警察叔叔 -Yes Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和明野 矢来三人一起玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人举报了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们小学也算大名远扬的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐也是在这个小镇上长大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 很小的小镇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们一起说话的时候不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但彼此都很了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在同一个小镇里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着同样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着同样的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听起来很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲身经历过昨天还一起笑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一转眼大家就生活在不同的时空里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然如此 就退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 喋喋不休地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和琴塚学姐容易说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看下原稿样品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经做完一本了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来文艺部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我多事了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总结了你不在的这几天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天象仪制作日志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了设计图哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始准备用布来做球顶的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果用纸板做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好以后大概是这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要制作投影仪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川同学好卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Punching 是指打孔的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要打500个以上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用洞的大小来控制星星的亮度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不容易哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经弄坏了一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上那边也有进展哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱子的设计很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是打孔 真是太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木的话应该会很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭那天能一起工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再一起去看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一瞬间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道该取什么名字好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜这每一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:46.27,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.48,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 照亮大地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:49.59,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
